OL,3,CResidents in over 55s block shocked at
OL,4,C100% increase for heating bills
OL,6,FThe residents of a block of flats in
OL,7,FSt Leonards in Sussex say they have
OL,8,Fbeen left in shock after their heating
OL,9,Fbills went up by 100%.
OL,11,FThe company running the site has sent
OL,12,Fout invoices showing the fixed weekly
OL,13,Fcharge for gas has doubled, but many
OL,14,Fresidents told ITV News Meridian they
OL,15,Fcan't afford the increase.
OL,17,FThose who live in Wyvern House in St
OL,18,FLeonards are over 55; some are
OL,19,Fpensioners, while others on universal
OL,20,Fcredit.
