OL,3,CResidents in over 55s block shocked at
OL,4,C100% increase for heating bills
OL,6,FFor many residents, money is tight due
OL,7,Fto the cost of living and now, they've
OL,8,Fbeen told each flat's gas bill has
OL,9,Frisen by 100%
OL,11,FLast year a two bedroom flat had to
OL,12,Fcontribute #21 per week towards gas
OL,13,Fand this year it has almost doubled to
OL,14,F#39.
OL,16,FThe site has a fixed price for
OL,17,Fresidents whether they use their
OL,18,Fheating or not.JPlaces for People,
OL,19,Fwhich runs Wyvern House, describes
OL,20,Fitself as the UK's leading social
OL,21,Fenterprise.
